---
title: "bid (AuctionBidder)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_access: require whenNotPaused, AUCTION_BIDDER_ROLE
    q_check_access --> q_get_auction: auction = s_auction
    q_get_auction --> q_get_assetout: assetOut = auction.getAssetOut()
    q_get_assetout --> q_check_solution: check solution.length
    q_check_solution --> q_encode_solution: solution.length > 0
    q_check_solution --> q_pre_approve: solution.length == 0
    q_pre_approve --> q_call_bid: forceApprove(auction, getAssetOutAmount(assetIn, amount, block.timestamp))
    q_encode_solution --> q_call_bid: data = encode(solution)
    q_call_bid --> q_check_leftover: auction.bid(assetIn, amount, data)
    q_check_leftover --> q_check_receiver: assetOutBalance > 0
    q_check_leftover --> [*]: assetOutBalance == 0
    q_check_receiver --> q_transfer_leftover: receiver != address(0)
    q_check_receiver --> [*]: receiver == address(0)
    q_transfer_leftover --> [*]: safeTransfer(receiver, assetOutBalance)

    note right of q_check_solution
        INV-001: With solution, callback executes arbitrary calls to source assetOut
        INV-002: Without solution, pre-approves exact assetOutAmount before bidding
        INV-003: Leftover assetOut is forwarded to configured receiver
    end note
